# Frontend Stack

- This repo uses Vite with React and React Router.
- Follow existing patterns before introducing a new structure.

# Canonical Files

- App shell and route rendering: `@src/App.jsx`
- Route definitions: `@src/routes.jsx`
- App bootstrap: `@src/main.jsx`

# Guidance

- Keep route additions aligned with `src/routes.jsx`.
- Prefer small, readable components that match the existing JSX style in `src/`.
- Keep guidance concrete and repo-specific; avoid adding generic frontend style-guide text here.
